---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Plasterers & Painters in Farnborough | Hancock' description='Plastering and painting in Farnborough. Fixed-price quotes from City & Guilds certified contractors covering Farnborough and the surrounding area.' activePage='areas'>
<section style="position:relative;height:340px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(3).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 40%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 48px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/areas" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Areas</a> / Farnborough</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,52px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Farnborough GU14</h1>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;">This area is not within our service corridor.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="background:#FEF2F2;border:1px solid #FECACA;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 28px;margin-bottom:32px;">
      <p style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#991B1B;margin:0 0 8px;">Not in our service area</p>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#7F1D1D;margin:0;line-height:1.65;">Farnborough GU14 is in Hampshire — approximately 40 miles from our base in Harefield. This is outside our service corridor. We don't cover it.</p>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Why this page exists</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">GU14 is Hampshire. We're Middlesex. That's 40 miles — not a trade run.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Hancock Plastering &amp; Painting Services is based in Harefield, UB9 6HF. Our service corridor runs from Stanmore and Watford in the north-east to Bracknell, Farnham, and Ascot in the south-west. Farnborough GU14 sits well outside that zone.</p>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">If you're in <strong>Farnham</strong> (our southernmost covered area), we can help — see the <a href="/areas/farnham" style="color:#0C7BA8;text-decoration:none;">Farnham page</a>. If you're looking for a local plasterer in Hampshire, you'll need someone based closer to GU14.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,36px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">In Middlesex or the Home Counties?</h2>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 28px;">We cover 26 areas across Middlesex, Hertfordshire, and Berkshire. See if your area's on the list.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/areas" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">View All Service Areas</a>
      <a href="/" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">Back to Homepage</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
